### Sync AvailableQuantity for all books

# Login as admin first
POST https://localhost:7125/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@elibrary.com",
    "password": "Admin@123"
}

###

# Sync available quantities for all books
POST https://localhost:7125/api/Book/admin/sync-quantities
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

# Check current books data after sync
GET https://localhost:7125/api/Book/admin/all
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

# Check available books (what users see) after sync
GET https://localhost:7125/api/Book/available
Content-Type: application/json